               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir "The Five Pillars of Mystery" (fols. 5r-34r)
                     
 I-1) Introduction (fols. 3r-16v) 
 I-2) Mǝśṭira Śǝllāse “Mystery of
                     the Trinity” (fols. 16v-38r) 
 I-3) Mǝśṭira śǝggāwe “Mystery of the
                     Incarnation” (fols. 38r-63r) 
 I-4) Mǝśṭira ṭǝmqat “Mystery of Baptism”
                     (fols. 63r-79r) 
 I-5) Mǝśṭira qʷǝrbān “Mystery of the Eucharist” (fols.
                     79r-93r 
 I-6) Mǝśṭira tǝnśāʾe mutān “Mystery of the Resurrection of the
                     Dead” (fols. 93r-109r)</summary>
